<Base title="Digital Marketing Conception" description="Digital marketing conception with relevance for consumer behaviour – Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">Strategy</p>
<h1>Digital Marketing Conception with Relevance for Consumer Behaviour</h1>
<p>Digital marketing conception is a strategy in e-commerce for various areas of life and market. For this, we create an ecosystem for e-commerce that is tailored to your business model and the customer habits of your market positioning. We use tools from Shopware 6 and additional software integrations for this.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Digital Marketing Conception by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Strategic market alignment needs digital marketing conception to reach your target group precisely. The prerequisite is an online shop that offers simple operation and as many opportunities for action and interaction as possible. We create digital competence here through as many automated processes and sensible infrastructures as possible.</p>
<h2>Digital Marketing Conception with Smooth Logistics and Unlimited Availability</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Optimal foundations:</strong> This detail is our special task. With the development of digital strategies, we present your business model in a market-relevant way technologically with automations, layout adaptations, scalings and the sensible building of a virtual infrastructure.</li>
<li><strong>Agile thinking processes:</strong> Only market practice shows whether you have thought ahead correctly. Budget and resources for future expansions must be determined and planned.</li>
<li><strong>Customer is key:</strong> You as the owner clearly know exactly what makes your products special. Informing, offering solutions, pricing and presentation according to target group needs all flow in here.</li>
<li><strong>Business plan metrics:</strong> In ongoing e-commerce, metrics on return rates, shipping and storage costs, framework contracts and supply chains as well as dealer networks are taken into account.</li>
<li><strong>Domain and trademark rights:</strong> For this you need a temporal and financial lead time to have your brand legally protected from imitators with details such as slogan, logo and domain.</li>
<li><strong>Corporate image with on-site presence:</strong> For all the love of digital commerce, those business models find high acceptance that also offer products available on site when interested.</li>
<li><strong>Percentage advantage over competitors:</strong> Quick overview when searching for products and a fast, simple ordering system are important for excellent process flows. Also considered are after-sales components such as returns, warranties and repair offers.</li>
<li><strong>What if scenarios:</strong> What if products are not deliverable, negative press makes the rounds or a shitstorm breaks out against product and provider? With the right digital concept, you are equipped for the worst case in e-commerce from the outset.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Digital Marketing Conception – as Versatile as Industry Expectations</h2>
<p>Digital marketing conception can be tailored for every industry from retail with everyday consumer goods to large corporations for innovative products for lifestyle, fashion, tourism, packaging, food and many more. Each concept always remains as authentic and individual as your entrepreneurial success goals for e-commerce.</p>
<h2>Benefits of Digital Marketing Conception by Hob by Horse for Your Target Groups</h2>
<p>Wholesalers and retailers benefit from strategically innovative digital marketing conception through quick access to information, services and products as well as clean ordering processes and market-relevant after-sale service. In B2C, simplicity and striking presentation alongside a fast, pleasant shopping experience are decisive for success.</p>
<p><em>Is digital marketing conception what you need for success with your online shop? Call Hob by Horse or exchange your concept ideas by <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">email</a>!</em></p>
</div></div>
